Response
In this capstone project, I'd like to analyze the
differences between New York city, Toronto and Tokyo,
with regards to venues information obtained from
Foursquare. I hope to observe how similar/dissimilar
these cities are and also where either two are similar
than the other two and think of why. Optionally, I may
identify what venues are missing compared to the
others to seek the "blue ocean venues area" in a city.


